responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "A27D12CB43C165FD9DF5F6A9C6FDD34D", "A shattered wagon lies in a stream at the base of the cliff, its splintered timbers and scattered debris the remnants of a caravan that once traveled the heights above.
